commitResults.messageBody: WIP working on editing the test cases to test for food instead of person

Some test cases are commented out to allow the team to move on with the
implementation of certain features and add relevant test cases to fit
the usage of wife instead of reusing AB3's test cases as some are
irrelevant

Commands are being categorised as:
1. foodcommands [all commands related to food]
2. tagcommands [all commands related to tags]
3. generalcommands [commands related to the general application itself,
   i.e., exit, help, etc.]

*same structure is used for test section.
Extract tagname out from `Tag` class as `TagName`

Test cases for `TagName` are:
1. check if tag name is empty (blank name)
2. check if tag name contains random symbol
3. check if tag name is too lengthy (> 15 characters long)

Remove the check of valid tag name from `Tag` class and all checking for
valid tag name convention is done by `TagName` class instead.

Add a function to help capitalize first letter of each word in a String
for standardization of names in WIFE.
